{
  "stem": "15732.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the way I persuaded him was by crying and-- and-- and and screaming, I want to live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That seemed to have been the-- the slogan then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were not many avenues open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my father had a friend who was how do you-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were not too many cinemas in Cernauti at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if there were-- three or four cinemas, most probably.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the biggest cinema.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was from the first that got an authorization that they needed him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was secure in his job that they would need him and he-- he wouldn't be taken away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can only remember his first name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was Salom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father had a good to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he agreed-- there was no remuneration in that involved at all-- he was a Jewish man-- to hide us in-- in the cinema, in a very-- in a small room, a dark room.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was all concrete.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very cold there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In time, my feet started-- I still have got, until today, frostbite from that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whenever it's cold, it starts to flare up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a tiny little window there-- it was more a hole than a window-- from which I could see how the-- pardon me-- how the Germans proceeded in the next deportations.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I saw them tearing the beards of the old Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I saw them beating-- oh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Basically, these were not Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were Romanians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans-- it-- those were not Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That were Romanians that did that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I forgot to tell you before was that at the beginning-- I'm sorry, if I can jump now--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
